Dear Officers of <%= @fund_request.organization %>,

This email is to inform you that your <%= @fund_request %> has been started, but requires further action before it will be considered submitted.

You may make changes to the fund_request here <<%= fund_request_fund_items_url(@fund_request) %>>.

When the fund_request is ready for submission, any of the following may approve it here <<%= new_polymorphic_url([@fund_request, 'approval']) %>>:

<% @fund_request.users.required_for_state('completed').each do |user| -%>
 * <%= user.name %>
<% end -%>

<% if @fund_request.fund_source.submissions_due_at && @fund_request.fund_source.submissions_due_at > DateTime.now -%>
The next deadline for submissions is <%= @fund_request.fund_source.submissions_due_at.to_s :us_ordinal %>.
<% end -%>

<% if @fund_request.fund_source.contact_web -%>
More information is available here <<%= @fund_request.fund_source.contact_web %>>.
<% end -%>

Sincerely,

<%= @fund_request.fund_source.contact_name %>

